it's not just a hobby.

42:50.735 --> 42:53.069
<i> It's something that</i>
<i> I can really succeed at.</i>

42:53.196 --> 42:54.404
I'm gonna use the $10,000

42:54.531 --> 42:56.281
and just put it straight
into a new shop,

42:56.408 --> 42:59.617
and these are, like,
my only pair of jeans.

42:59.744 --> 43:01.119
So maybe I'll get
another pair of jeans.

43:01.246 --> 43:02.704
[chuckles]

